script='for i in $(seq 314 -1 1); do pattern="$(echo -n . | rps "$(( i % 10 ))")"; replacement="$(printf -- "%s" "$pattern" | sed "s=\.= =g")"; echo "$message" | sed "s/$pattern\$/$replacement/"; done | lolcat -f | sed -u "s=\(.\)\(\[38\)=\1[44m\1\2=g"'
